OL,3,CSNP only party 'serious about winning'
OL,4,CHolyrood election, Swinney claims
OL,6,FThe SNP is the only party "serious
OL,7,Fabout winning" the Scottish Parliament
OL,8,Felection, the First Minister has
OL,9,Fclaimed.
OL,11,FJohn Swinney claimed Labour had now
OL,12,F"given up the pretence" that it was
OL,13,Ftrying to win a majority at Holyrood.
OL,15,FHe repeated his claims that Scottish
OL,16,FLabour leader Anas Sarwar wanted to do
OL,17,Fa deal with Reform to become first
OL,18,Fminister ` something both parties deny.
OL,26,@nD@[OUoD@NO]tD@AOUtD@WO]
