OL,3,CSNP only party 'serious about winning'
OL,4,CHolyrood election, Swinney claims
OL,6,FHe said an SNP majority at Holyrood
OL,7,Fwould lock out the "politics of Nigel
OL,8,FFarage" from power in Scotland.
OL,10,FMr Swinney said his party was the only
OL,11,Fone with a "serious plan" for Scotland.
OL,13,FHe accused Labour and Reform of having
OL,14,F"nothing to say" on the "energy crisis
OL,15,Fhammering households".
OL,26,@oD@TOUpD@GO]sD@LOUsD@YO]vD@AOUvD@PO]vD@
OL,26,AYOUwD@UO]
