OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775369052
OL,3,CSNP only party 'serious about winning'
OL,4,CHolyrood election, Swinney claims
OL,6,F"Over the first full week of this
OL,7,Felection campaign, it has been clear
OL,8,Fthat the SNP is the only party with a
OL,9,Fserious plan for Scotland's future and
OL,10,Fis the only party serious about
OL,11,Fwinning," the First Minister said.
OL,13,F"On the biggest issue of the day ` the
OL,14,Fenergy crisis hammering households in
OL,15,FScotland ` Reform and Labour have had
OL,16,Fnothing to say.
OL,18,F"Labour on both sides of the border
OL,19,Fare standing by and doing nothing
OL,20,Fwhile people in Scotland suffer.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]uD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775369052
OL,3,CSNP only party 'serious about winning'
OL,4,CHolyrood election, Swinney claims
OL,6,F"Labour has also given up on any
OL,7,Fpretence that they are seeking to
OL,8,Factually win the election ` their
OL,9,Fenergy is now focused entirely on
OL,10,Fensuring they have the numbers to do a
OL,11,Fdeal with Nigel Farage and the Tories
OL,12,Fafter the election.
OL,14,F"That is one of the reasons that I am
OL,15,Fso determined to secure an SNP
OL,16,Fmajority.
OL,18,F"The politics of Nigel Farage and
OL,19,FReform have no place in our society
OL,20,Fand an SNP majority will lock them out
OL,21,Fof power.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
