PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775369052
OL,3,CSNP only party 'serious about winning'
OL,4,CHolyrood election, Swinney claims
OL,6,F"And crucially, an SNP majority will
OL,7,Funlock the fresh start of independence
OL,8,Fthat will allow us to bring down
OL,9,Fenergy bills and make sure Scotland's
OL,10,Fenergy wealth works for us, rather
OL,11,Fthan flowing to the UK Government."
OL,13,FScottish Conservative deputy leader
OL,14,FRachael Hamilton said: "This election
OL,15,Fshould be about the cost-of-living but
OL,16,FJohn Swinney only wants to talk about
OL,17,Findependence.
OL,19,F"We know that if the SNP get a
OL,20,Fmajority, Swinney will use it as a
OL,21,Fmandate to break up the United Kingdom.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@cO]vD@XOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
