PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775369052
OL,3,CSNP only party 'serious about winning'
OL,4,CHolyrood election, Swinney claims
OL,6,F"This is not some distant threat. The
OL,7,Fdanger of an SNP majority is very real.
OL,9,F"But Scots can stop it, just like we
OL,10,Fdid in 2016 and 2021.
OL,12,F"John Swinney thinks he's got this
OL,13,Felection in the bag, but you can stop
OL,14,Fhim by voting Scottish Conservative on
OL,15,Fyour peach ballot paper.
OL,17,F"That's your secret weapon to stop an
OL,18,FSNP majority."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOUzD@NO]
