OL,3,CSNP only party 'serious about winning'
OL,4,CHolyrood election, Swinney claims
OL,6,FScottish Labour's deputy leader Dame
OL,7,FJackie Baillie said: "John Swinney's
OL,8,Farrogance is breathtaking.
OL,10,F"This election is our first real
OL,11,Fchance in nearly 20 years to change
OL,12,Fthe Scottish government and it is not
OL,13,Fa chance we can afford to miss.
OL,15,F"Scottish Labour is determined to get
OL,16,Frid of this tired and complacent SNP
OL,17,Fgovernment and deliver a better future
OL,18,Ffor Scotland.
OL,26,@oD@VOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
