OL,3,CSNP only party 'serious about winning'
OL,4,CHolyrood election, Swinney claims
OL,6,F"On May 7 we can reject Reform and
OL,7,Fvote for change by electing a Scottish
OL,8,FLabour government that will get the
OL,9,Fbasics right in our public services
OL,10,Fand make life more affordable for
OL,11,FScots."
